A long shot, but...

My Cruzbike was nicked this evening at around 20:00 from outside a house in
Maiden Erlegh, Reading.  It's very distinctive, a front wheel drive
recumbent just like this...

http://www.cruzbike.com/sofrider.html

...mine had a seatpost rack with panniers and  very bright LED lights.  I
think it's the only prodcuction Cruzbike in the country, being imported from
Oz via the USA.  I was just getting to like it too.  I suspect local scrotes
have trashed it and dumped it in the lake, but in case anyone should see it,
I'm on zkeit ... @zneonicaz.co.uk without the zeds.

Cheers
